  "detailed_description": "Little Big Guy is a third-person small-scale survival game.<br />\r\nYou can collect resources by researching around and craft new items.<br />\r\nSurvive<br />\r\nIt takes food, drink and rest to survive.<br />\r\nTools can be made by gathering resources and you can use them for hunting, farming or fishing.<br />\r\nBase Building<br />\r\nWild animals and undead monsters will be found around.You need a safe place to protect yourself.You can also have your various stations here.<br />\r\nMaps<br />\r\n2 maps are waiting to be explored.",
